# Sync Job Registry to Desktop

After any operation that modifies the Fuyao job registry (~/.cursor/tmp/fuyao_job_registry.json), push it to huh.desktop.us:

```bash
scp ~/.cursor/tmp/fuyao_job_registry.json huh.desktop.us:~/software/Experiment-Tracker-/fuyao_job_registry.json
```

This applies after:
- Job registration via deploy-fuyao or sweep-fuyao skills
- Registry add, remove, clear, protect, unprotect, or sync operations
- Any batch registry update

The push is non-blocking. If it fails (SSH unreachable), warn and continue.
